sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SRV  as 2030.5 Server
    participant C    as C Binary
    participant PY   as Python Bridge
    participant MB   as Modbus Device

    Note over SRV,C: event delivery (poll or notification)

    SRV ->> C: DERControl {mrid, start, duration, DERControlBase}
    C   ->> C: schedule at start_time

    Note over C,PY: EVENT_START

    C   ->> PY: EVENT_JSON: {type:start, mrid:abc123,<br/>duration:900, control:{opModFixedW:8000, rampTms:60}}

    PY  ->> PY: bridge.apply(event) → RegisterMap

    PY  ->> MB: write_register(40100, 8000)   # active_power
    MB  -->> PY: ok
    PY  ->> MB: write_register(40103, 60)     # ramp_time
    MB  -->> PY: ok
    Note over PY: _active_registers = {40100:8000, 40103:60}

    rect rgb(40, 80, 60)
        Note over SRV,MB: ... 900 seconds ...
    end

    Note over C,PY: EVENT_END

    C   ->> PY: EVENT_JSON: {type:end, mrid:abc123}

    PY  ->> PY: bridge._relinquish()

    loop for each address in _active_registers
        PY  ->> MB: write_register(address, 0)
        MB  -->> PY: ok
    end
    Note over PY: _active_registers = {}
